      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0031"/><hi rend="latintype">Welt-</hi><hi rend="pre-print">Po<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tkarte</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler (aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs>)</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb959">Marienlyst</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb43570">Dänemark</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0032"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs>, <date when="1906-07-13">13. Juli</date>.
                  <salute>Lieber Freund,</salute> Nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43570">Dänemark</rs> komme ich nicht – ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>uche wieder<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tarke
               Gebirgsluft auf u.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chwanke noch zwi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43435">Schweiz</rs> u. <rs type="place" ref="#pmb423">Tirol</rs>.
               K<unclear>ä</unclear>me<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Du nicht vielleicht nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43570">Dänemark</rs> noch ins <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03248-1"/>Gebirge<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03248-1">Dazu kam es nicht.</note>? Ich
               würde mich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr freuen, <del rend="strikethrough">Dich</del><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><del rend="strikethrough"><unclear>da</unclear></del> irgendwo mit Dir <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03248-2"/>zu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ammenzutreffen<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03248-2"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11485">Goldmann</rs> trafen sich erst am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1907-05-24" subtype="date-only"/> in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs> wieder.</note>. Herzliche Grüße Dir u.
               Deiner <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">Frau</rs> von Deinem
               getreuen <signed>Paul Goldmann.</signed></p><postscript><p>Was macht <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb12692">Heinrich Schnitzler</rs></hi>?</p></postscript></div>
      </body>
